product_name: Hennessy Hammock Explorer Deluxe Asym Classic Hammock
long_description: At 10 ft. long, the Explorer Deluxe Asym Classic from Hennessy Hammock is designed for anyone under 300 lbs. or up to 7 ft. tall. This comfortable hammock sets up in about 3 minutes.
